OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening in the north with a few
OL,7,Fshowers, dry with clear spells
OL,8,Felsewhere. Becoming cloudier for all
OL,9,Fovernight with outbreaks of rain in
OL,10,Fthe north. Light northwesterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA cloudy day with outbreaks of
OL,13,Frain in the morning spreading
OL,14,Fsouthwards through the day to reach
OL,15,FSkye and Lochaber later in the
OL,16,Fafternoon. Drier in the north later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
